videos.description: After the Rockets fall behind 3-1 in their series against the Lakers, James Harden is short with his answers to the media about Houston's effort level.

videos.description: Russell Westbrook believes everyone, including himself, must make big sacrifices from this point on in order to bounce back from a 3-1 deficit vs. the Lakers.
